  "actionable_ascii_heavy_residuals": [],
  "accepted_ascii_heavy_residuals": [
    {
      "item_id": "d2dabf697b:1",
      "text": "RenderManProcedural (RiProcedural)",
      "ascii_letters": 31,
      "cjk_chars": 0
    },
    {
      "item_id": "d2dabf697b:2",
      "text": "RenderMan for Maya 随附通用 procedural node type RenderManProcedural，可用于加载 RiProcedural 子例程（不是 RiProcedural2）。它的设计目标是快速、简单，不需要安装或 custom 定制。为了提高灵活性，可以使用 Pre Shape Mel attribute 在 scene translation 期间设置 string data 参数。",
      "ascii_letters": 129,
      "cjk_chars": 51
    },
    {
      "item_id": "d2dabf697b:3",
      "text": "Custom Nodetype Extensions (RiProcedural and RiProcedural2)",
      "ascii_letters": 51,
      "cjk_chars": 0
    },
    {
      "item_id": "d2dabf697b:4",
      "text": "或者，用户可以使用 .args 文件参数列表，为任意 Maya nodes 指定到 DSO procedurals 的 custom 映射。这旨在让 RenderMan 与现有 Maya plug-ins 无缝集成。",
      "ascii_letters": 53,
      "cjk_chars": 34
    },
    {
      "item_id": "d2dabf697b:5",
      "text": "Environment Configuration",
      "ascii_letters": 24,
      "cjk_chars": 0
    },
    {
      "item_id": "d2dabf697b:6",
      "text": "可以在以下位置放置 config/mayaTranslation.json extension file，让 RfM 识别 custom .args 文件 procedurals：",
      "ascii_letters": 62,
      "cjk_chars": 14
    },
    {
      "item_id": "d2dabf697b:8",
      "text": "。示例 site configuration（站点配置）：",
      "ascii_letters": 17,
      "cjk_chars": 6
    },
    {
      "item_id": "d2dabf697b:10",
      "text": "每个 path 都应包含 procedural，以及一个",
      "ascii_letters": 14,
      "cjk_chars": 10
    },
    {
      "item_id": "d2dabf697b:14",
      "text": "中的 paths 会被加入 render-time search paths，包括以下 sub paths：",
      "ascii_letters": 34,
      "cjk_chars": 10
    },
    {
      "item_id": "d2dabf697b:15",
      "text": "Nodetype Mapping",
      "ascii_letters": 15,
      "cjk_chars": 0
    },
    {
      "item_id": "d2dabf697b:16",
      "text": "该目录应包含 config/mayaTranslation.json，用于声明 translator mappings。在这个例子中，我们把 custom Maya nodetype \"MayaSphere\" 映射到 RenderMan procedural \"SphereProc\"。示例 config/mayaTranslation.json：",
      "ascii_letters": 125,
      "cjk_chars": 24
    },
    {
      "item_id": "d2dabf697b:17",
      "text": "RfM 和 RenderMan 会在 RFM_SITE_PATH 与 RFM_SHOW_PATH 中搜索指定名称的 procedurals DSOs 和 Args，也就是 SphereProc.so 与 SphereProc.args。",
      "ascii_letters": 79,
      "cjk_chars": 17
    },
    {
      "item_id": "d2dabf697b:18",
      "text": "Procedural Args File",
      "ascii_letters": 18,
      "cjk_chars": 0
    },
    {
      "item_id": "d2dabf697b:19",
      "text": "args 文件应将 plug-in typeTag 设置为 \"procedural\"（用于 RiProcedural）或 \"procedural2\"（用于 RiProcedural2）。还必须把特殊的 \"string __dsoname\" 参数设置为 DSO 的名称。其他 procedural parameter 可以像 shading parameters 一样声明。\"match\" feature 可用于翻译参数名不同的 Maya attributes，例如：",
      "ascii_letters": 139,
      "cjk_chars": 49
    },
    {
      "item_id": "d2dabf697b:20",
      "text": "Example Download",
      "ascii_letters": 15,
      "cjk_chars": 0
    },
    {
      "item_id": "d2dabf697b:21",
      "text": "带有 RenderMan procedural integration 的示例 Maya plug-in：",
      "ascii_letters": 40,
      "cjk_chars": 5
    },
    {
      "item_id": "d2dabf697b:22",
      "text": "simple_procedural.zip",
      "ascii_letters": 19,
      "cjk_chars": 0
    },
    {
      "item_id": "d2dabf697b:23",
      "text": "Late Material Binding",
      "ascii_letters": 19,
      "cjk_chars": 0
    },
    {
      "item_id": "d2dabf697b:24",
      "text": "Materials 可以使用这里描述的 __materialid 机制进行 late bound：",
      "ascii_letters": 28,
      "cjk_chars": 13
    },
    {
      "item_id": "d2dabf697b:25",
      "text": "/wiki/spaces/REN/pages/19859939",
      "ascii_letters": 18,
      "cjk_chars": 0
    },
    {
      "item_id": "d2dabf697b:26",
      "text": "。在 Maya 中，\"string __materialid\" 参数对应 Maya shading group 名称。用户可能需要在 render settings 的 Advanced 区域下启用 \"Output All Shaders\"，以便预先输出所有 materials。",
      "ascii_letters": 83,
      "cjk_chars": 29
    }
  ],
